      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "> So reindex is not counted as \"warmup\" but should be, instead?\n\nNo, I don't think so.\nRemember reindex can take a long time on the main chain, we have no reason for RPC to be available in the mean time. The warmup phase exists because it would be **unsafe** to offer RPC functionality (e.g. everything expects pcoinsTip to be populated).\n\nI wouldn't be against adding a `reindex_in_progress` status field to some RPC call though.\n",
